    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在《符文秘术师》中精通玄奥秘法</strong><br>——这是一款 rogue-like 动作游戏，你的每个选择都将铸就自己的命运。作为最后的秘术师，你即是抵御蔓延黑暗的利刃。手握禁忌知识与诅咒之钢，你必须深入地下城——那里每道阴影皆藏尖齿，每条廊道皆因遗忘之罪的重量而扭曲盘绕！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179460/extras/508d23f274c2c8dc186e2045a644eacd.poster.avif?t=1772094477\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179460/extras/508d23f274c2c8dc186e2045a644eacd.webm?t=1772094477\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179460/extras/508d23f274c2c8dc186e2045a644eacd.mp4?t=1772094477\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179460/extras/26a8b096011d1a09c68a6fd198c7f693.avif?t=1772094477\" width=1200 height=144 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多样武器库<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179460/extras/930c46fb14d6acbe8f29623b1a993fc9.avif?t=1772094477\" width=1200 height=477 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >操控各具特色的独特武器，每种皆拥有不同的特性与攻击机制。每把武器不仅提供独特战斗风格，更能与你的构筑选择产生多样的协同效应。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >深度构筑系统<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179460/extras/4c8803abdb67c834499677d83655695a.avif?t=1772094477\" width=1200 height=440 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >构筑体系以“符文”和“卡牌”为核心，结合角色机制与游戏实体系统形成复杂互动。随着每次冒险推进，你的构筑将不断进化蜕变。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >可控随机与程序生成</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179460/extras/7a3a86e57f24f94152fc8ae8d3a4664d.poster.avif?t=1772094477\" width=1170 height=638 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179460/extras/7a3a86e57f24f94152fc8ae8d3a4664d.webm?t=1772094477\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179460/extras/7a3a86e57f24f94152fc8ae8d3a4664d.mp4?t=1772094477\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >掌控混沌的秩序。世界虽由程序生成，但你始终拥有选择权。探索新生区域、迎战未知敌人——每次征程都绝不重复！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >动态战斗系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179460/extras/696e56c0e74d0d47261004aef382c074.poster.avif?t=1772094477\" width=1170 height=638 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179460/extras/696e56c0e74d0d47261004aef382c074.webm?t=1772094477\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179460/extras/696e56c0e74d0d47261004aef382c074.mp4?t=1772094477\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >充满挑战却蕴含智慧的作战机制中，死亡不仅是挫折，更是揭示远古知识、推动进程的关键所在。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>完成仪式……或至死方休！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179460/extras/ccba74401cffd7054fc7c812e1335b97.poster.avif?t=1772094477\" width=1170 height=638 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179460/extras/ccba74401cffd7054fc7c812e1335b97.webm?t=1772094477\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179460/extras/ccba74401cffd7054fc7c812e1335b97.mp4?t=1772094477\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179460/extras/2e21bb361b6f228735d2c030b65c7dd0.avif?t=1772094477\" width=1200 height=144 /></span></p>",
